text: Newburg is an unincorporated community in Fillmore County, in the U.S. state of Minnesota. ==History== Newburg was platted in 1853. A post office was established at Newburg in 1855, and remained in operation until it was discontinued in 1902. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Fillmore County, Minnesota Category:Unincorporated communities in Minnesota
title: Newburg, Minnesota
